Revision history for Perl extension Dancer2::Serializer::XML.

0.05  2018-08-08
	- Allow configuration to be passed while invoking the module. Allow the use of "send_as XML" core method.
  - Specify build_requires to eliminate CPAN test failures

0.04  2017-02-19
	- Switch Changes file to ISO date format
	- Remove a few unused classes in module
	- Remove Test::More from inside test class to silence warning
	- Remove perl version requirement from Makefile.PL

0.03  2017-02-18
	- Header fix in docs

0.01  2017-02-19
	- First version

